  "id": "MGASA-2021-0164",
  "summary": "Updated thunderbird packages fix security vulnerabilities",
  "details": "Texture upload into an unbound backing buffer resulted in an out-of-bound read.\n(CVE-2021-23981)\n\nAngle graphics library out of date. (CVE-2021-4127)\n\nInternal network hosts could have been probed by a malicious webpage. (CVE-2021-23982)\n\nMalicious extensions could have spoofed popup information. (CVE-2021-23984)\n\nMemory safety bugs fixed in Thunderbird 78.9. (CVE-2021-23987)\n",
